opendial.domains.rules

Class RuleCase

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.domains.rules.RuleCase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RuleOutput

    public class RuleCase
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a rule case, containing a condition and a list of alternative effects if the condition holds. Each alternative effect has a distinct probability or utility parameter.
    Author:
    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)
